I'm here to help! I currently have the following tools at my disposal:

1. Weather Check: You can ask me for the current weather in a specific city, like this:
   {"name": "get_weather", "arguments": {"city": "Antwerp"}}

2. File Search: This allows you to find files based on patterns within your project directory.
   {"name": "search_files", "arguments": {"pattern": "*.py"}}

3. Meeting Scheduler: You can organize meetings with participants at a particular time.
   {"name": "schedule_meeting", "arguments": {"title": "Team Meeting", "time": "10:00 AM EST"}}
